      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BREAKOUT LAD (3) is better than last start when seventh (26.07) in a Grade 5 at this track over 457m. Form here sound including four wins. Form from his last run is proving strong. Has ability and looks hard to stop. CASH ON DEMAND (1) failed to come into contention last start at this track, but prior to that won by a neck at this track (19.61) beating Slack in a Mix 5 on January 28. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings six times from eight starts. Has ability and can atone. STRIKES TWICE (2) comes off an average performance last start when seventh at Q Straight over 350m behind Hey Ernie (19.41) in a Mix 5. Key player if finds best. DIVORCE PAPERS (7) was in the money last start despite a big quote and is likely to feature again.",
